<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />For Yahweh's word is upright,</para>

<para style="q1">and everything he does is fair.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />He loves righteousness and justice.</para>

<para style="q1">The earth is full of Yahweh's covenant faithfulness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />By the word of Yahweh the heavens were made,</para>

<para style="q1">and all the stars were made by the breath of his mouth.</para>
